menu "Web server test configuration"

config WEB_SERVER_TEST_QEMU_MODE
    bool "Skip hardware and network init (QEMU mode)"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, skips WiFi, motor, tracing, and web server setup so the
        test binary runs under QEMU. Hardware-dependent test cases report
        TEST_IGNORE instead of blocking on missing peripherals.

endmenu
